snippet.title: Full Fathom - Official Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Full Fathom is an oceanic survival horror game. Pilot a deteriorating submarine as it drifts through grim waters, keeping it maintained as it is your only lifeline in the hostile, merciless ocean.
Full Fathom is now available to wishlist on Steam!
